Interface EncryptedRecord

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Signable, SignedDocument<EncryptedRecord>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocalEncryptedRecord

    public interface EncryptedRecord
extends Signable, SignedDocument<EncryptedRecord>
    A record holding encrypted data, plus a signature. Consider using the LocalEncryptedRecord implementation.
